Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.50,0:00:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.53,0:00:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…行…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.93,0:00:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}若是那時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.01,0:00:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川同學未曾出現
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.51,0:00:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.78,0:00:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}一定會…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.77,0:00:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沖繩那時候還真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.32,0:00:32.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就差一點了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.33,0:00:33.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再一點兒…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.98,0:00:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…不好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.79,0:00:50.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.01,0:00:53.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不可以忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…來到這個星球是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.95,0:01:05.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又故障了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.42,0:01:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.49,0:01:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.72,0:01:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 又在幹嘛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.42,0:02:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘎哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.63,0:03:01.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}外星人送來的大怪獸！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}MIA導彈發射
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.50,0:03:30.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們在拍什麼電影來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.61,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別問我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.18,0:03:35.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你啊 在這電影裡死幾回了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:36.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這我咋知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.34,0:03:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.09,0:03:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.33,0:03:42.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不休息一下嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.41,0:03:44.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給 石垣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.07,0:03:46.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:47.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人也請用
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.16,0:03:49.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.60,0:03:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝…謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.65,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 我還在洗衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:04:00.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…請加油哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}發生什麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.11,0:04:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}「什麼」是啥？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.38,0:04:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和一夏學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.86,0:04:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有啊…還…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.48,0:04:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.30,0:04:16.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 對了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我得去拿攝影機
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.63,0:04:18.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}先去下二樓…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.16,0:04:22.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:32.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.92,0:04:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說 你昨天去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.53,0:04:43.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自從去了沖繩回來 就有點怪怪的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.09,0:04:47.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過終端的狀況這麼不好…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.43,0:04:49.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的沒事嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.48,0:04:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.18,0:04:58.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天的晚飯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.60,0:05:00.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就做漢堡肉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.76,0:05:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那好像海人是最喜歡吃的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}反正我…我也喜歡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.17,0:05:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}理音？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.21,0:05:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接…接吻？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.48,0:05:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}笨蛋 聲音太大了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐還在呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.73,0:05:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}親了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.02,0:05:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…與其說是親了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不如說是要親了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.87,0:05:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…就差一點來著
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.53,0:05:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒親啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.23,0:05:30.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我不說了就差一點點了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.57,0:05:34.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜真可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}DEAD END確立了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.18,0:05:37.81,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}其實這裡是指走到盡頭了 字面說法一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.89,0:05:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我也沒辦法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我也不知道你講的是真的還是假的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.47,0:05:44.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是真的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.12,0:05:46.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.39,0:05:50.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你啊…是想撮合我和谷川嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.82,0:05:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就別太…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:55.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.62,0:05:56.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.02,0:05:59.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喲 這邊這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.45,0:06:00.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:01.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.04,0:06:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.37,0:06:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我來送洗好的膠卷了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.31,0:06:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.08,0:06:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像是因為摻進了一種「高感光膠卷」
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.03,0:06:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以洗起來比較花時間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.43,0:06:13.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原…你那髮型…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:16.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 這個？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為很熱嘛 又想換個形像就剪了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.72,0:06:21.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}會很奇怪嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.20,0:06:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不會 很合適很合適
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.77,0:06:26.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是吧 哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.39,0:06:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.76,0:06:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.73,0:06:34.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.22,0:06:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.26,0:06:37.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}北原同學
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.32,0:06:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果真是北原同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.14,0:06:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剪頭髮了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.65,0:06:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好適合你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.22,0:06:45.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這衣服也很配你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.95,0:06:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}謝謝誇獎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.67,0:06:48.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}稍等一下哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:50.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我馬上端茶過去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.39,0:06:51.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.72,0:06:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那進來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}膠卷啊 就特攝的部分
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.34,0:06:55.48,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}特技攝影的簡寫 諸如奧特曼 假面騎士等稱為特技攝影
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.50,0:06:57.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嘗試著剪輯了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.23,0:06:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.81,0:07:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.72,0:07:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}吶 哪兒哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.29,0:07:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.57,0:07:04.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}還差一點點
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.23,0:07:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天沒關係的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.93,0:07:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.48,0:07:09.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎麼了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:11.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.89,0:07:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 沒什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.65,0:07:18.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}今天試著做了一下冰淇淋
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.60,0:07:20.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}自己做的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 因為是第一次所以有點擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.83,0:07:26.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過看起來好好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.47,0:07:27.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.61,0:07:29.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}話說原來冰淇淋還能自己做啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.12,0:07:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奈美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.93,0:07:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你…還在當高中生啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.43,0:07:50.14,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}喂喂！真相了啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.61,0:07:52.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}因為我可是永遠的17歲啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.48,0:07:54.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.44,0:07:57.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在這裡也就是說…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.09,0:07:59.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又和小倉學長吵架了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.49,0:08:02.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那傢伙…居然把我買的遊戲先過關了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.09,0:08:05.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}而且還從頭劇透到尾
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.59,0:08:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}關係依舊這麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.31,0:08:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哪裡好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.14,0:08:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}比起這個 怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}說有事是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.82,0:08:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.08,0:08:16.50,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}秘密筆記
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.95,0:08:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還真是錯綜複雜呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.97,0:08:22.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.94,0:08:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有些事想要學姐來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.75,0:08:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哼~你在打什麼算盤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.50,0:08:32.23,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}美櫻→哲朗→柑菜→海人→一夏 我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.05,0:08:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那再見咯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.41,0:08:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.93,0:08:37.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.90,0:08:43.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}感覺…美櫻好像變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.16,0:08:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不僅是髮型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.43,0:08:47.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.55,0:08:48.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}問她為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.57,0:08:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}她也只是說「不知不覺」而已
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.37,0:08:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗你有什麼頭緒嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.88,0:08:55.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}柑菜你都不知道我可能知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}唔 也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.07,0:09:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人也是…好像變了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.32,0:09:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.54,0:09:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}知道了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.69,0:09:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.26,0:09:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.39,0:09:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}後天就有廟會了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.56,0:09:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.38,0:09:25.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}像去年那樣大家再一起去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.54,0:09:27.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再邀請上貴月學姐和檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.10,0:09:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.46,0:09:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實我讓美櫻的媽媽幫我做了浴衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.30,0:09:34.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}成套的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.44,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}帶子是粉色的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.91,0:09:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好可愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.71,0:09:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以說別隨便摸女孩子的頭髮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.51,0:09:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}所以說別摸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.22,0:09:46.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是嗎是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:48.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.23,0:10:00.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這就是…最初邂逅的時候啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.39,0:10:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這時候…我大概已經…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.64,0:10:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.81,0:10:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是夜空啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.22,0:10:14.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那時候照的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.99,0:10:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}果然大都照…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.03,0:10:19.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.94,0:10:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人 飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.82,0:10:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.02,0:10:26.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.33,0:10:49.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好慢啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.08,0:10:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}在幹嘛呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哲朗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.32,0:10:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}哦 這就是上次說的那個浴衣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.74,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 不錯嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是人靠衣裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.34,0:11:01.41,zhushi,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}日本諺語馬子にも衣裝 大概就是人靠衣裝馬靠鞍
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.14,0:11:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好疼！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.11,0:11:03.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再說我就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}可惡 那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.46,0:11:10.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我覺得你 還是坦誠一些比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.20,0:11:12.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我已經很坦誠了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.18,0:11:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}如果不這樣…傳達不到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.30,0:11:25.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不太會穿這個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.30,0:11:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}花了些時間
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.14,0:11:30.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是姿色過人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.34,0:11:32.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是…好棒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:34.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是…是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.09,0:11:36.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不過又是姐姐的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.44,0:11:37.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}穿得習慣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.77,0:11:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}又是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.30,0:11:42.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}喂 你在幹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.93,0:11:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大家都到齊了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.45,0:11:43.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}趕快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.91,0:11:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.83,0:11:45.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.64,0:11:48.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}所以我不是叫你別摸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.55,0:11:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這 這就是廟會！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.50,0:11:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那 總之先逛個一圈…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.46,0:11:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在說什麼啊 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.60,0:12:01.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}要說廟會的妙趣 非那個莫屬吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.19,0:12:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯 就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.28,0:12:05.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.03,0:12:10.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是這個~！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.40,0:12:13.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}來 嚐一嚐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這是 什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.25,0:12:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特棒了！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.69,0:12:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特棒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.50,0:12:41.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 特棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.79,0:12:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}廟會什麼的特棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.16,0:12:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還真是挺樂在其中的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.86,0:12:47.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.03,0:12:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}特棒了~
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}學姐 下一個想去哪兒？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.20,0:12:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？叫我怎麼選啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.82,0:12:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}每個攤位都特給力了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:56.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.50,0:12:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸檬學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.00,0:13:01.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看來你們很享受夏季廟會呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.86,0:13:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}就是啊 檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.27,0:13:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}廟會真的特棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.58,0:13:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不 還不夠哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.53,0:13:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還不夠
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.64,0:13:12.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這還不能說是充分享受了夏季廟會
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.54,0:13:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}還有什麼嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.00,0:13:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是什麼啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.23,0:13:17.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那就是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.47,0:13:20.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試膽大會哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:24.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}試膽大會是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.92,0:13:26.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 該怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.96,0:13:28.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是個很簡單的遊戲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.89,0:13:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}先登上那階梯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.37,0:13:34.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}然後在頂上的祠堂裡供上符紙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.03,0:13:35.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}再回來而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.73,0:13:36.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.42,0:13:40.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我對恐怖的有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.24,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒問題哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.67,0:13:44.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們會根據抽簽分成兩人一組
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.94,0:13:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}海人~
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.54,0:13:54.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}請務必來玩吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.31,0:13:56.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你們這麼肯參加
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.43,0:13:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我很開心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.05,0:13:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.23,0:14:05.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}神…神啊 十分感謝！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.38,0:14:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}接著只要挑個好時機
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.88,0:14:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.74,0:14:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好像碰到了什麼蟲子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.35,0:14:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}呃 真的十分抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:20.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然和我想像中的有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:20.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我們走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.97,0:14:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是這樣也有戲！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:29.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}什麼都沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.81,0:14:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但 但是我好像看到了什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.94,0:14:34.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒有啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.88,0:14:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但是但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.24,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}妖怪 幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.38,0:14:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}亡者的靈魂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.42,0:14:43.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其在現世彷徨遊蕩的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.77,0:14:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}雖然有傳說以及目擊的案例
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.42,0:14:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}但在科學上卻未被證明過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.90,0:14:50.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:53.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那是從人類的恐懼心和迷信中所生的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是想像出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.38,0:14:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.01,0:15:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸…檬…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.36,0:15:04.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.47,0:15:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}有怪莫怪…有怪莫怪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.01,0:15:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這反應真不錯哦 一夏
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.44,0:15:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}{\an8}對不起…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:11.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 接下來是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.32,0:15:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}好 搞定
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.96,0:15:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}看吧 什麼事都沒有吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.42,0:15:24.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.81,0:15:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那麼 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.01,0:15:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.56,0:15:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}和你一組的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.67,0:15:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}其實你是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}吶 我說你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.78,0:15:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你那髮型…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.36,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}怎…怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.77,0:15:43.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊…貌似
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.36,0:15:56.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛…剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.84,0:15:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是哲朗他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.94,0:16:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.35,0:16:02.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.28,0:16:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有點…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.91,0:16:06.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.67,0:16:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}大…大家都沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.18,0:16:17.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}到底怎麼了 剛才那個聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.63,0:16:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的跑哪裡去了啊 檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我說你們 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.48,0:16:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啊 沒想到你們會嚇成那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.21,0:16:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真沒禮貌啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.47,0:16:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}是我啦我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}姐…姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.47,0:16:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真奈美姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:56.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你腦子裡在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個…為試膽大會助興？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.10,0:17:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}別開玩笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.48,0:17:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}真是的 用不著那麼生氣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.24,0:17:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}抱歉啦 美櫻醬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.56,0:17:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}啊不 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.49,0:17:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}抱歉你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.87,0:17:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}{\blur5}我這不都道歉了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}幹的好 真奈美學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:17.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}那個 谷川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:20.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}差不多該…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.93,0:17:21.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}阿海…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.34,0:17:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.57,0:17:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷…川
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}檸…檸檬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.44,0:17:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.43,0:17:37.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.27,0:17:39.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.48,0:17:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}有沒有誰在 海人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.76,0:17:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}剛才的是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.65,0:17:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}這個
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.27,0:17:54.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur5}谷川你別走開
